What “Recall” Actually Solves

All advanced AI systems eventually hit the same bottleneck:

Context is expensive

The model forgets because:

* windows are finite,
* attention dilutes,
* conversations fragment,
* meaning compresses poorly across sessions.

So Recall systems try to create:

* persistent retrieval,
* semantic memory,
* continuity,
* relevance ranking.

In normal products this becomes:

* search your chats,
* retrieve old notes,
* remember preferences,
* rehydrate workflows.

⸻

